The '''Visayan Academy of Arts and Letters''' ({{Lang-ceb|Akademyang Bisaya}}) is a [[Philippines|Philippine]] [[language regulator]] whose aims are to preserve and to develop the [[Cebuano language]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sunstar.com.ph/cebu/akademiyang-bisaya-launched-effort-promote-language |title=Archived copy |access-date=2009-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091020013859/http://www.sunstar.com.ph/cebu/akademiyang-bisaya-launched-effort-promote-language |archive-date=2009-10-20 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref> In this regard, the [[Commission on the Filipino Language]] shares the same mission.<ref>http://wika.pbworks.com/Misyon%20at%20Bisyon</ref>

